reviews.review:
Positives;
Great with friends, I feel like to get into the game more that you need friends. Its hard to get good at the game but when you do its awesome. Climbing the ranks feels very fulfilling (even tho ranks barley mean anything). DLCs are not too pricey and super fun to use.

Negatives;
Hard to learn. Not so fun to play solo most of the time. Matchmaking will match you with people that aren't your skill level a LOT. Ranks mean barley anything.
